name: Mazda CX 5
description: The 2017 Mazda CX-5 is an excellent choice for a reliable, practical, and stylish crossover SUV. The CX-5 is one of the most fuel-efficient SUVs on the market and offers an impressive level of standard features. It has an attractive interior with comfortable, supportive seats, and an array of advanced technologies like blind spot monitoring, adaptive cruise control, and a rearview camera.
